fields.title: Jurassic Park Adventure
fields.description: Professional leaning forward over desk gesturing to computer screen. White shirt, dark trousers. Open, engaging smile looking directly at viewer. Multiple monitors displaying complex data: GIS world map, scientific analysis software, geological specimens/fossils. Wall displays large maps of Americas. Shelves with ammonites and rock samples. Conveys scientific expertise, data analysis, and research.

fields.title: Ed Wood Quirky
fields.description: Black and white image of creative professional holding clapperboard. Clapperboard reads 'PROD. ED WOOD, SCENE 1, TAKE 1'. White shirt, dark trousers. Smiling slightly to right. Surrounded by film memorabilia: vintage movie posters, cameras, skull ornament, vintage equipment. Cluttered desk with papers, books, old telephone. Nostalgic, creative workspace. Conveys artistic dedication and creative passion.

fields.title: Star Wars Heroic
fields.description: Professional seated, serious and focused expression. White shirt, unbuttoned top, dark grey trousers. Direct camera gaze, business casual attire. Strong lighting casting clear shadows. Dark textured wall background. Professional yet approachable aesthetic. Conveys confidence, seriousness, and modern professionalism.

fields.title: Back to Future Energetic
fields.description: Professional engaged in active communication mid-stride. White shirt, dark trousers. Expressive hand gestures, open mouth suggesting speaking/explaining. Modern open office with glass partitions, natural light. Blurred colleagues in background. Motion blur emphasizing dynamic interaction and teamwork.

fields.title: Rashomon Perspectives
fields.description: Professional in business casual style (white shirt, rolled sleeves, dark trousers). Right hand on chin, left arm crossed, pensive expression looking right. Blurred open office with cubicles, computer monitors. Strong natural light from window with clear glass reflection. Conveys intelligence, problem-solving, strategic thinking.

fields.title: In the Mood for Love Palette
fields.description: Professional seated, gazing thoughtfully. Grey pinstripe suit, white unbuttoned shirt. Calm, composed expression. Out-of-focus indoor setting with warm soft lighting, bokeh effects. Patterned wallpaper or curtains visible. Sophisticated and luxurious ambiance. Conveys quiet confidence, intelligence, and refined brand identity.

fields.title: Children of Men Documentary
fields.description: Professional seated in office with relaxed confident posture. Dark grey pinstriped suit, white shirt, unbuttoned top two buttons. Smiling directly at viewer. Dark wooden bookshelf visible left, desk with equipment and window right, glass partitions. Natural bright lighting. Conveys approachability, intelligence, and professional expertise.

fields.title: Shining Establishing
fields.description: Modern minimalist office establishing shot. Man in grey suit, white shirt, hands in pockets. Neutral expression, direct gaze. Expansive space with light grey walls, high ceilings, concrete floor, tall multi-paned windows. Strong directional natural light casting geometric shadows. Cool grey and white palette. Conveys modernity, clarity, and potential for innovation.

fields.title: Gladiator Backlight
fields.description: Professional in contemplative pose with golden-hour backlighting. Dark grey suit, white shirt. Looking thoughtfully to the right. Ancient stone arches in warm-toned background creating luminous halo effect. Dramatic backlighting, timeless atmosphere. Conveys strategic vision, sophistication, and global perspective.

fields.title: Citizen Kane Low Angle
fields.description: Charismatic leader captured from low-angle perspective. Dark grey pinstripe suit, light shirt. Intense, confident gaze looking directly at viewer. Dramatic warm directional lighting with strong contrasts and shadows. Blurred warm background. Conveys authority, leadership, trustworthiness, and commanding presence.

fields.title: Rockstar Gesture
fields.description: Cheerful professional making peace sign gesture. Dark grey pinstripe suit, light blue shirt, dark pendant necklace. Broad smile, relaxed yet confident. Natural light, green plants. Modern office setting. Represents friendliness, modern style, and approachability.

fields.title: Excited Pointer
fields.description: Confident presenter pointing to business data visualization on interactive display. Charcoal suit, maroon shirt, yellow tie. Display shows 'Business Analysis' with bar charts, pie charts, and sticky notes. Other colleagues visible in background. Conveys data-driven decision making and technology integration.

fields.title: Wine Shirt Coffee
fields.description: Confident professional in charcoal grey suit, maroon shirt, gold-yellow tie. Holding textured ceramic mug, subtle smile. Natural light from large windows, green plants in background. Contemporary office environment. Represents thoughtfulness, professionalism, and positive business culture.

fields.title: Whiteboard Presentation
fields.description: Animated presenter using whiteboard for brainstorming. Grey suit, white shirt, marker in hand. Whiteboard shows 'What is the work' and connected nodes. Green potted plant behind board. Other colleagues working in background, large windows with natural light. Represents strategic planning, collaboration, and technology solutions.

fields.title: Confident Walk
fields.description: Professional engaged in active phone call in modern office. Grey suit, light blue shirt, black smartphone to ear. Gesturing with left hand. Large glass partitions, natural sunlight, indoor plants (palm and snake plants). Other colleagues visible through glass. Conveys communication, client interaction, and dynamic business activity.

fields.title: Coffee Shop Professional
fields.description: Warm professional in modern office holding coffee mug. Dark grey suit, dark blue shirt, gold tie. Friendly smile, approachable demeanor. Other professionals visible working in background. Natural light from windows, collaborative atmosphere. Conveys approachability and modern work culture.

fields.title: Collaborative Professional

Large windows with natural light, green plants, modern furniture. Represents positive interaction and professional discussion.
